  "title": "7506 - Beauty Therapist (Slimming Therapist cum Consultant)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Basic Salary Range: $ 2500 - $ 3500 + Commission</li>\n  <li>Address: Orchard </li>\n  <li>Working Hours: 10am – 8pm (2 hours lunch break)</li>\n  <li>Working Days: 5 days work week rotational shift, must be willing to work on weekend</li>\n  <li>Benefits: AL &amp; MC as per MOM standard</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 1 year of experience in the slimming industry - facial industry can be considered too.</li>\n  <li>Certifications in body / aesthetic / beauty and facial technique knowledge will be a plus.</li>\n  <li>Proven track record of sales experience with knowledge in postpartum wellness and slimming may be considered for a senior role.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver slimming treatments using advanced machines to help clients achieve their desired results.</li>\n  <li>Establish strong rapport with clients, ensuring they feel valued and supported throughout their journey.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and track clients' progress closely, offering personalized guidance and encouragement along the way.</li>\n  <li>Educate clients on available products and treatments, assisting them in making informed decisions.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a clean and organized workspace, guaranteeing a safe and hygienic environment for clients.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with team members to optimize customer satisfaction and retention.</li>\n  <li>Stay updated on industry trends and best practices to enhance service delivery.</li>\n  <li>Handle client inquiries and concerns with professionalism and empathy.</li>\n  <li>Assist in administrative tasks such as appointment scheduling and record-keeping.</li>\n  <li>Adhere to company policies and procedures, ensuring compliance at all times.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Chin See Min Reg No. : R22107450</strong></p>\n<p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No. : 14C7279</strong></p>",
